common

Enum DigitalSignature

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<DigitalSignature>
      • common.DigitalSignature
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<DigitalSignature>

    public enum DigitalSignature
extends java.lang.Enum<DigitalSignature>
    Enumerates known image formats by identifying their distinct magic numbers in the image file header. These magic numbers reside in the first few bytes of the file.
    Since:
    13 August 2025
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Trevor Maggs
